  <p>
    The browser will store the received
    <code>last-modified</code>
    date and will include it on every subsequent request using the
    <code>if-modified-since</code>
    request header. If the data is older than the
    <code>if-modified-since</code>
    value, then the server will respond with a
    <code>304</code>
    status code.
  </p>
